backblocks
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the sparsely settled hinterland of more closely-settled districts
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: also back-country, the boohai, the sticks
Pronunciation:
Notes: aka back blocks, back-blocks
